data.description: Start the next chapter in your life in your dream home in the heart of Franklin Township.   Enjoy open-concept living between the living room, kitchen, & dining room, making entertaining & daily life a breeze. Appreciate preparing meals in the updated kitchen, featuring new cabinets, modern appliances, sleek countertops, & ample storage space. Be prepared to be delighted by the master bathroom, complete with contemporary fixtures and a modern design. Beyond the aesthetics, this home is equipped with newer mechanicals - HVAC 2020, water heater 2017, & Kinetico softener. Nestled on a generous .37-acre lot with a fully-fenced backyard, it is a great place to enjoy time outside. All of your storage worries will melt away with the new large storage barn with loft. This residence promises a lifestyle of serenity and freedom, unburdened by the constraints of an HOA.  Check it out today!
